how to auto load kernel modules when system boot up?
man modules-load.d

/etc/modules-load.d/jusss.conf
bbswitch
fat
vfat
msdos
nls_cp437
ntfs
vboxnetadp
vboxnetflt
vboxpci
vboxdrvw

and set modules parameters /etc/modprobe.d/jusss.conf
options module parameter

also you can black it on that file too
